wdi2-NY.TTF.GNFS.KN.def: The terms of trade effect equals capacity to import less exports of goods and services in constant prices. Data are in constant local currency.
wdi2-NY.TTF.GNFS.KN.name: Terms of trade adjustment
wdi2-NY.TTF.GNFS.KN.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
